statements: SELECT * FROM regulatory_documents;
SELECT document_id, document_type, document_date FROM regulatory_documents WHERE status='approved';
SELECT * FROM regulatory_documents WHERE document_type='license' ORDER BY document_date DESC;
SELECT document_id, document_type, document_date, status FROM regulatory_documents WHERE status='pending' ORDER BY document_date ASC;
SELECT document_id, document_type, document_date, expiration_date FROM regulatory_documents WHERE expiration_date >= CURDATE();
SELECT * FROM regulatory_documents WHERE document_type = 'Certificate of Title' ORDER BY document_date DESC
SELECT document_id, document_type, document_date FROM regulatory_documents WHERE status = 'approved' AND property_id = 12345
SELECT document_type, COUNT(*) AS num_documents FROM regulatory_documents GROUP BY document_type HAVING num_documents > 10 ORDER BY num_documents DESC
SELECT property_id, MAX(document_date) AS latest_document_date FROM regulatory_documents GROUP BY property_id
SELECT property_id, AVG(DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE, document_date)) AS avg_days_since_document FROM regulatory_documents GROUP BY property_id ORDER BY avg_days_since_document DESC
SELECT * FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents;
SELECT document_name, document_type FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents ORDER BY document_name DESC;
SELECT document_name, document_type, LENGTH(document_content) AS content_length FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents WHERE document_type='Regulatory';
SELECT compliance_id, compliance_type, compliance_status FROM compliance_information WHERE property_id = 12345;
SELECT document_name, SUBSTRING(document_content, 1, 50) AS partial_content FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents ORDER BY document_name LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents WHERE document_type='Legal' ORDER BY document_name DESC
SELECT document_id, document_name FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents WHERE document_id > 100
SELECT compliance_id, compliance_type, compliance_status FROM compliance_information WHERE compliance_status='Pending' ORDER BY compliance_id
SELECT * FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents WHERE document_id IN (1, 3, 5)
SELECT document_name, document_type FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents WHERE document_type='Financial'
SELECT document_id, document_name FROM RealEstateDocuments;
SELECT document_name, document_type, document_date FROM RealEstateDocuments;
SELECT compliance_id, property_id, compliance_status FROM ComplianceInformation;
SELECT requirement_name FROM LegalRequirements;
SELECT * FROM RealEstateDocuments WHERE document_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT * FROM RealEstateDocuments WHERE document_type = 'Contract' ORDER BY document_date DESC;
SELECT document_name, document_type FROM RealEstateDocuments WHERE document_date >= '2022-01-01' AND document_date <= '2022-12-31';

SELECT document_name, compliance_status, compliance_date FROM RealEstateDocuments rd INNER JOIN ComplianceInformation ci ON rd.document_id = ci.property_id WHERE rd.document_type = 'Agreement' AND ci.compliance_status = 'Pending';
SELECT rd.document_name, ci.responsible_person FROM RealEstateDocuments rd INNER JOIN ComplianceInformation ci ON rd.document_id = ci.property_id WHERE rd.document_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT lr.requirement_name, lr.requirement_description FROM RealEstateDocuments rd, LegalRequirements lr WHERE rd.document_type = 'Report';
SELECT * FROM property_information;
SELECT property_name, property_address FROM property_information WHERE property_type = 'Residential';
SELECT document_id, document_name, document_date FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents ORDER BY document_date DESC;
SELECT compliance_id, compliance_type, compliance_status FROM compliance_information WHERE compliance_status = 'Pending' ORDER BY compliance_due_date;
SELECT buyer_name, seller_name, transaction_amount FROM transaction_information WHERE transaction_amount > 100000 ORDER BY transaction_amount DESC;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents WHERE document_type = 'Building Permit' ORDER BY document_date DESC;
SELECT document_name, document_type FROM real_estate_regulatory_documents WHERE document_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT compliance_id, compliance_type, compliance_status FROM compliance_information WHERE compliance_status = 'Compliant' ORDER BY compliance_due_date;
SELECT property_name, property_address, property_type FROM property_information WHERE property_type = 'Residential' LIMIT 10;
SELECT transaction_id, property_id, buyer_name, seller_name, transaction_amount FROM transaction_information WHERE transaction_amount > 10000 ORDER BY transaction_amount DESC;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_documents;
SELECT document_name, document_type, document_date FROM real_estate_documents;
SELECT property_name, property_value FROM property_details ORDER BY property_value DESC;
SELECT owner_name, compliance_date FROM compliance_information WHERE compliance_status = TRUE;
SELECT requirement_name, requirement_description FROM legal_requirements WHERE requirement_deadline > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM real_estate_documents ORDER BY document_date DESC, document_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT document_id, document_name, document_type FROM real_estate_documents WHERE document_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT property_name, property_address, property_value FROM property_details WHERE property_value > 100000 ORDER BY property_value DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT owner_name, compliance_status FROM compliance_information WHERE compliance_date < '2022-06-01';
SELECT requirement_id, requirement_name, requirement_deadline FROM legal_requirements WHERE requirement_deadline < '2022-08-01';
